---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us">
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative min-h-[716px] flex items-center overflow-hidden px-12 py-24">
<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30 grayscale contrast-125" data-alt="abstract digital network connection nodes and blue data streams flowing through deep space background with atmospheric lighting" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCMz5d0lqlW4oc27W7bRBblxgEZB6-5kcCBW12ktF88BDbiPHRqPr_RkxFDWSL_kzm-9mDmyGIF3mDrUxoWz5YEBk_Esnekd9yqxMDCqK2NJMC-6713iLAN249DTquknfmQMof74YsY3YowPiwY6Vrwoo5Kpa2R2tBPnmppvmRUpl8CXb1jecEIsbvrcxBFYFOQWIajcSqfjhqjp9fuK-_DtsCy_MFwO3eRLrJZxaygeLfR_qd_jHtJ0uKW0wNm0npaUCtSldy-7jU7"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-surface via-surface/80 to-transparent"></div>
</div>
<div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl max-w-[1440px] mx-auto w-full">
<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-secondary-container/30 border border-outline-variant/15 rounded-full text-primary-fixed-dim text-xs font-label tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">
<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed-dim animate-pulse"></span>
Architecting the Future
</div>
<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl xl:text-8xl font-bold leading-[0.9] tracking-tighter font-bold font-headline mb-8 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                    Intelligent Systems.<br/>
<span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-fixed-dim to-on-primary-container">Unified Progress.</span>
</h1>
<p class="text-xl text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
                    VEINTECH is a technology company focusing on developing integrated systems, AI-based automation, and digital solutions. We bridge the gap between complex infrastructure and seamless operational intelligence.
                </p>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Vision & Mission Asymmetric Grid -->
<section class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-12 py-32">
<div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-8">
<!-- Vision Card -->
<div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-7 relative bg-surface-container-low p-12 rounded-xl overflow-hidden group border border-outline-variant/15">
<div class="node-indicator"></div>
<div class="relative z-10">
<span class="text-primary-fixed-dim material-symbols-outlined text-4xl mb-6" data-icon="visibility">visibility</span>
<h2 class="text-4xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">Our Vision</h2>
<p class="text-2xl text-on-surface leading-tight font-light italic">
                            "Helping organizations transform digitally through intelligent system integration and automation."
                        </p>
</div>
<div class="absolute -right-20 -bottom-20 w-80 h-80 opacity-5 group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity duration-700">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[300px]" data-icon="hub">hub</span>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Mission Card -->
<div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-5 bg-surface-container p-12 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-primary-fixed-dim/20">
<h2 class="text-3xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-8">Our Mission</h2>
<ul class="space-y-6">
<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim mt-1" data-icon="account_tree">account_tree</span>
<div>
<span class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white block mb-1">Scalable Solutions</span>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Building architectures that grow alongside your global ambitions.</p>
</div>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim mt-1" data-icon="speed">speed</span>
<div>
<span class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white block mb-1">Business Process Optimization</span>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Eliminating bottlenecks through algorithmic precision.</p>
</div>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim mt-1" data-icon="integration_instructions">integration_instructions</span>
<div>
<span class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white block mb-1">Efficient Integration</span>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Connecting disparate data silos into a unified nervous system.</p>
</div>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim mt-1" data-icon="psychology">psychology</span>
<div>
<span class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white block mb-1">AI &amp; Automation Adoption</span>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Lowering the barrier for next-generation intelligence integration.</p>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Core Values (VECTOR) - Bento Grid Style -->
<section class="bg-surface-container-lowest py-32 px-12 border border-outline-variant/15">
<div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto">
<div class="mb-16 text-center">
<h2 class="text-5xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-tighter">The VEINTECH Principles</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant mt-4">The core values that define every line of code we write.</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
<!-- V -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors relative overflow-hidden group border border-outline-variant/15">
<div class="text-8xl font-black font-headline text-white/5 absolute -right-4 -top-4 group-hover:text-primary-fixed-dim/10 transition-colors">V</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-headline font-bold text-primary-fixed-dim mb-4">Visionary</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">We look beyond the immediate requirements to build solutions that remain relevant in the decades to come.</p>
</div>
<!-- E -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors relative overflow-hidden group border border-outline-variant/15">
<div class="text-8xl font-black font-headline text-white/5 absolute -right-4 -top-4 group-hover:text-primary-fixed-dim/10 transition-colors">E</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-headline font-bold text-primary-fixed-dim mb-4">Efficient</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Maximum output with minimal resource overhead. Performance is not a feature; it's our baseline.</p>
</div>
<!-- C -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors relative overflow-hidden group border border-outline-variant/15">
<div class="text-8xl font-black font-headline text-white/5 absolute -right-4 -top-4 group-hover:text-primary-fixed-dim/10 transition-colors">C</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-headline font-bold text-primary-fixed-dim mb-4">Collaborative</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">We integrate not just systems, but with your team, becoming a natural extension of your technical department.</p>
</div>
<!-- T -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors relative overflow-hidden group border border-outline-variant/15">
<div class="text-8xl font-black font-headline text-white/5 absolute -right-4 -top-4 group-hover:text-primary-fixed-dim/10 transition-colors">T</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-headline font-bold text-primary-fixed-dim mb-4">Technology Driven</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Utilizing the latest breakthroughs in AI and distributed computing to solve age-old business problems.</p>
</div>
<!-- O -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors relative overflow-hidden group border border-outline-variant/15">
<div class="text-8xl font-black font-headline text-white/5 absolute -right-4 -top-4 group-hover:text-primary-fixed-dim/10 transition-colors">O</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-headline font-bold text-primary-fixed-dim mb-4">Optimization</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Continuous improvement is hardcoded into our culture. We refine until perfection becomes efficiency.</p>
</div>
<!-- R -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors relative overflow-hidden group border border-outline-variant/15">
<div class="text-8xl font-black font-headline text-white/5 absolute -right-4 -top-4 group-hover:text-primary-fixed-dim/10 transition-colors">R</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-headline font-bold text-primary-fixed-dim mb-4">Reliable</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Uptime, security, and consistent performance. Systems you can trust with your most critical operations.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Glassmorphism Stats/Trust Section -->
<section class="relative py-24 px-12 overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-50" data-alt="macro close-up of computer server circuits and flashing led lights in a dark server room environment" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuA32xnINGepG8IKBUaYooqgf21e5zU6DXfpEM_yMBYL_ncPgI7sqaQAmuhLg-VC5jU2PteLt9HpRYT2k3PcnRpGVjfY2lriRQF0kOA9FK1q2-4QVQ609VdWm5R7Wh6WTqEu4DUIEtWvkB1CgBnFsNK3vdzmcrkDhxuWvoFbUSp-pj2oTnmWfaUgNkrCssPvCm-coGjW9DmFSNmeDLPDhBygAMIQxoRF6WeqBCrCECAufpcx253yDEda501Q9uG9fYKCw8sF-GLfTKBf"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-surface/90"></div>
</div>
<div class="relative z-10 max-w-[1440px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
<div class="p-8 bg-surface-container/60 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-lg text-center border border-white/5">
<div class="text-5xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">500+</div>
<div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-fixed-dim">Systems Integrated</div>
</div>
<div class="p-8 bg-surface-container/60 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-lg text-center border border-white/5">
<div class="text-5xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">99.9%</div>
<div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-fixed-dim">Success Rate</div>
</div>
<div class="p-8 bg-surface-container/60 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-lg text-center border border-white/5">
<div class="text-5xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">12ms</div>
<div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-fixed-dim">Avg. Latency Reduced</div>
</div>
<div class="p-8 bg-surface-container/60 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-lg text-center border border-white/5">
<div class="text-5xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">24/7</div>
<div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-fixed-dim">Active Monitoring</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</BaseLayout>
